revious century kept the piece on the stage for the next fifty years, and in anthologies up to the present.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4aEnglish literature. 4aJohn Dryden. 4adrama. 4aliterature. 4aplays. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / English, Irish, Scottish, Welsh.2bisacsh1 aDearing, Vinton A., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000z97831106353480 cprintz978052008766840uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052091512140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520915121423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520915121/original  a978-3-11-063534-8  University of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles